r name the angels female names,"}},"28":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.87","c":"وَمَا","d":"āَmَw","e":"āَmَw"},{"b":"0.66","h":"1.83","c":"لَهُمْ","d":"mُhَl","e":"mُhَl"},{"b":"2.1","h":"3.19","c":"بِهِ","d":"ۦِhِb","e":"ۦِhِb"},{"b":"2.9","h":"4.28","c":"مِنْ","d":"ْnِm","e":"ْnِm"},{"b":"3.3","h":"4.84","c":"عِلْمٍ","d":"ٍmْlِʿع","e":"ٍmْlِʿع"},{"b":"4.4","h":"6.34","c":"إِنْ","d":"nِiʾ","e":"nِiʾ"},{"b":"5.8","h":"7.39","c":"يَتَّبِعُونَ","d":"َnwُʿعِbَّtَy","e":"َnwُʿعِbَّtَy"},{"b":"7.2","h":"9.69","c":"إِلَّا","d":"āَّlِiʾ","e":"āَّlِiʾ"},{"b":"7.8","h":"10.74","c":"الظَّنَّ","d":"َّnَّẓlٱ","e":"َّnَّẓlٱ"},{"b":"9.5","h":"13.85","c":"وَإِنَّ","d":"َّnِiʾَw","e":"َّnِiʾَw"},{"b":"10.9","h":"15.49","c":"الظَّنَّ","d":"َّnَّẓlٱ","e":"َّnَّẓlٱ"},{"b":"12.3","h":"17.32","c":"لَا","d":"āَl","e":"āَl"},{"b":"12.7","h":"17.98","c":"يُغْنِي","d":"àِnْغُy","e":"àِnْغُy"},{"b":"13.7","h":"19.49","c":"مِنَ","d":"َnِm","e":"َnِm"},{"b":"14.1","h":"20.05","c":"الْحَقِّ","d":"ِّqَḥْlٱ","e":"ِّqَḥْlٱ"},{"b":"15.0","h":"21.43","c":"شَيْئًا","d":"āًٔـْyَhs","e":"āًٔـْyَhs"}],"a":{"g":"And they have thereof no knowledge. They follow not except assumption, and indeed, assumption avails not against the truth at all."}},"29":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.75","c":"فَأَعْرِضْ","d":"ْḍِrْʿعَaʾَf","e":"ْḍِrْʿعَaʾَf"},{"b":"1.0","h":"2.17","c":"عَنْ","d":"nَʿع","e":"nَʿع"},{"b":"2.0","h":"3.39","c":"مَنْ","d":"nَّm","e":"nَّm"},{"b":"2.8","h":"4.37","c":"تَوَلَّى","d":"ٰàَّlَwَt","e":"ٰàَّlَwَt"},{"b":"3.9","h":"6.33","c":"عَنْ","d":"nَʿع","e":"nَʿع"},{"b":"5.0","h":"7.44","c":"ذِكْرِنَا","d":"āَnِrْkِhd","e":"āَnِrْkِhd"},{"b":"6.1","h":"9.25","c":"وَلَمْ","d":"ْmَlَw","e":"ْmَlَw"},{"b":"6.8","h":"10.1","c":"يُرِدْ","d":"ْdِrُy","e":"ْdِrُy"},{"b":"7.5","h":"11.19","c":"إِلَّا","d":"āَّlِiʾ","e":"āَّlِiʾ"},{"b":"8.1","h":"12.15","c":"الْحَيَوةَ","d":"َẗٰwَyَḥْlٱ","e":"َẗٰwَyَḥْlٱ"},{"b":"9.3","h":"14","c":"الدُّنْيَا","d":"āَyْnُّdlٱ","e":"āَyْnُّdlٱ"}],"a":{"g":"So turn away from whoever turns his back on Our message and desires not except the worldly life.","ihya":"\n        <div class=\"ihya-tafsir-box\" style=\"margin-top: 15px; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 10px;\">\n            <h5 style=\"color: #91740c; font-family: Cabin, sans-serif;\">Tafsir Al-Ihya</h5>\n            <div class=\"ihya-arabic\" style=\"font-family: IndoPak; font-size: 18px; text-align: right; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #555;\">\n                ولما انكشف لأولياء الله تعالى أن العبد مهلك نفسه بأعماله واتباعه هوى نفسه إهلاك دود القز نفسه: رفضوا الدنيا بالكلية، حتى قال الحسن: رأيت سبعين بدرياً كانوا فيما أحل الله لهم أزهد منكم فيما حرم الله عليكم. وفي لفظ آخر: كانوا بالبلاء أشد قرحاً منكم بالخصب والرخاء لو رأيتموهم قلتم مجانين، ولو رأوا خياركم قالوا ما لهؤلاء من خلاق، ولو رأوا أشراركم قالوا ما يؤمن هؤلاء بيوم الحساب. وكان أحدهم يعرض لهم المال الحلال فلا يأخذه ويقول: أخاف أن يفسد على قلبي، فمن كان له قلب فهو لا محالة يخاف من فساده، والذين أمات حب الدنيا قلوبهم فقد أخبر الله عنهم إذ قال تعالى: \" فأعرض عمن تولى عن ذكرنا ولم يرد إلا الحياة الدنيا، ذلك مبلغهم من العلم\"، فأحال ذلك كله على الغفلة وعدم العلم.\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"ihya-english\" style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; color: #777;\">\n                Indeed, when it was unveiled [inkashafa] for the friends [awliya'] of God, the Exalted, that the servant destroys his own soul [nafs] by his actions and his following of his soul's [nafs] desire [hawa]—like the silkworm destroying itself—they rejected the world [dunya] completely. So much so that Al-Hasan said: \"I saw seventy of the Companions of Badr; they were, in what God had made lawful for them, more abstinent than you are in what God has forbidden for you.\" And in another wording: \"They were in hardship more wounded than you are in ease and plenty. If you saw them, you would say, 'They are madmen,' and if they saw the best of you, they would say, 'These have no share [khalāq],' and if they saw the worst of you, they would say, 'These do not believe in the Day of Reckoning.'\" And one of them would be offered lawful wealth and would not take it, saying, \"I fear it will corrupt my heart [qalb].\" For whoever possesses a heart [qalb] inevitably fears its corruption. And those whose hearts [qulub] have been killed by the love of the world [dunya]—God has informed about them when He, the Exalted, said: \"So turn away from him who turns away from Our Remembrance and desires nothing but the life of this world [dunya]. That is the extent of their knowledge ['ilm].\" He attributed all of that to heedlessness [ghafla] and the absence of knowledge ['ilm].\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        "}},"30":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.8","c":"ذَلِكَ","d":"َkِlَٰhd","e":"َkِlَٰhd"},{"b":"0.89","h":"1.98","c":"مَبْلَغُهُمْ","d":"mُhُغَlْbَm","e":"mُhُغَlْbَm"},{"b":"3.0","h":"4.33","c":"مِنَ","d":"َnِّm","e":"َnِّm"},{"b":"3.3","h":"5.22","c":"الْعِلْمِ","d":"ِmْlِʿعْlٱ","e":"ِmْlِʿعْlٱ"},{"b":"4.6","h":"7.95","c":"إِنَّ","d":"َّnِiʾ","e":"َّnِiʾ"},{"b":"5.7","h":"8.98","c":"رَبَّكَ","d":"َkَّbَr","e":"َkَّbَr"},{"b":"6.5","h":"10.42","c":"هُوَ","d":"َwُh","e":"َwُh"},{"b":"7.0","h":"11.13","c":"أَعْلَمُ","d":"ُmَlْʿعَaʾ","e":"ُmَlْʿعَaʾ"},{"b":"7.9","h":"12.58","c":"بِمَنْ","d":"nَmِb","e":"nَmِb"},{"b":"9.2","h":"14","c":"ضَلَّ","d":"َّlَḍ","e":"َّlَḍ"},{"b":"9.8","h":"14.8","c":"عَنْ","d":"nَʿع","e":"nَʿع"},{"b":"10.7","h":"15.9","c":"سَبِيلِهِ","d":"ۦِhِlyِbَs","e":"ۦِhِlyِbَs"},{"b":"12.1","h":"18.19","c":"وَهُوَ","d":"َwُhَw","e":"َwُhَw"},{"b":"12.8","h":"19.15","c":"أَعْلَمُ","d":"ُmَlْʿعَaʾ","e":"ُmَlْʿعَaʾ"},{"b":"13.7","h":"20.59","c":"بِمَنِ","d":"ِnَmِb","e":"ِnَmِb"},{"b":"14.3","h":"21.57","c":"اهْتَدَى","d":"ٰàَdَtْhٱ","e":"ٰàَdَtْhٱ"}],"a":{"g":"That is their sum of knowledge. Indeed, your Lord is most knowing of who strays from His way, and He is most knowing of who is guided."}},"31":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.47","c":"وَلِلَّهِ","d":"ِhَّlِlَw","e":"ِhَّlِlَw"},{"b":"1.4","h":"2.18","c":"مَا","d":"āَm","e":"āَm"},{"b":"1.7","h":"2.83","c":"فِي","d":"àِf","e":"àِf"},{"b":"2.0","h":"3.17","c":"السَّمَاوَاتِ","d":"ِtَٰwَٰmَّslٱ","e":"ِtَٰwَٰmَّslٱ"},{"b":"3.6","h":"5.58","c":"وَمَا","d":"āَmَw","e":"āَmَw"},{"b":"4.3","h":"6.59","c":"فِي","d":"àِf","e":"àِf"},{"b":"4.6","h":"7.06","c":"الْأَرْضِ","d":"ِḍْrَaʾْlٱ","e":"ِḍْrَaʾْlٱ"},{"b":"5.5","h":"10.05","c":"لِيَجْزِيَ","d":"َàِzْjgَyِl","e":"َàِzْjgَyِl"},{"b":"6.7","h":"11.49","c":"الَّذِينَ","d":"َnyِhdَّlٱ","e":"َnyِhdَّlٱ"},{"b":"7.8","h":"13.12","c":"أَسَاءُوا","d":"۟āwُٔـَٰٓsَaʾ","e":"۟āwُٔـَٰٓsَaʾ"},{"b":"10.8","h":"15.69","c":"بِمَا","d":"āَmِb","e":"āَmِb"},{"b":"11.4","h":"16.5","c":"عَمِلُوا","d":"۟āwُlِmَʿع","e":"۟āwُlِmَʿع"},{"b":"12.5","h":"18.1","c":"وَيَجْزِيَ","d":"َàِzْjgَyَw","e":"َàِzْjgَyَw"},{"b":"13.5","h":"19.55","c":"الَّذِينَ","d":"َnyِhdَّlٱ","e":"َnyِhdَّlٱ"},{"b":"14.7","h":"21.23","c":"أَحْسَنُوا","d":"۟āwُnَsْḥَaʾ","e":"۟āwُnَsْḥَaʾ"},{"b":"15.8","h":"22.92","c":"بِالْحُسْنَى","d":"àَnْsُḥْlٱِb","e":"àَnْsُḥْlٱِb"}],"a":{"g":"And to Allah belongs whatever is in the heavens and whatever is in the earth - that He may recompense those who do evil with [the penalty of] what they have done and recompense those who do good with the best [reward] -","ihya":"\n        <div class=\"ihya-tafsir-box\" style=\"margin-top: 15px; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 10px;\">\n            <h5 style=\"color: #91740c; font-family: Cabin, sans-serif;\">Tafsir Al-Ihya</h5>\n            <div class=\"ihya-arabic\" style=\"font-family: IndoPak; font-size: 18px; text-align: right; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #555;\">\n                هنالك تجزى كل نفس بما كسبت إن الله عز وجل يقول \"ليجزى الذي أساءوا بما عملوا ويجزى الذي أحسنوا بالحسنى\"\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"ihya-english\" style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; color: #777;\">\n                Indeed, there, every soul [nafs] will be recompensed for what it has earned. Indeed, Allah, the Mighty and Majestic, says: \"That He may recompense those who did evil for what they did, and recompense those who did good with the best [al-husna].\"\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        "}},"32":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.75","c":"الَّذِينَ","d":"َnyِhdَّlٱ","e":"َnyِhdَّlٱ"},{"b":"1.2","h":"2.47","c":"يَجْتَنِبُونَ","d":"َnwُbِnَtْjgَy","e":"َnwُbِnَtْjgَy"},{"b":"2.8","h":"4.77","c":"كَبَائِرَ","d":"َrِyʾَٰٓbَk","e":"َrِyʾَٰٓbَk"},{"b":"5.5","h":"7.11","c":"الْإِثْمِ","d":"ِmْhtِiʾْlٱ","e":"ِmْhtِiʾْlٱ"},{"b":"6.4","h":"8.37","c":"وَالْفَوَاحِشَ","d":"َhsِḥَٰwَfْlٱَw","e":"َhsِḥَٰwَfْlٱَw"},{"b":"8.0","h":"10.76","c":"إِلَّا","d":"āَّlِiʾ","e":"āَّlِiʾ"},{"b":"8.7","h":"11.7","c":"اللَّمَمَ","d":"َmَmَّllٱ","e":"َmَmَّllٱ"},{"b":"10.1","h":"16","c":"إِنَّ","d":"َّnِiʾ","e":"َّnِiʾ"},{"b":"11.4","h":"17.3","c":"رَبَّكَ","d":"َkَّbَr","e":"َkَّbَr"},{"b":"12.3","h":"18.7","c":"وَاسِعُ","d":"ُʿعِsَٰw","e":"ُʿعِsَٰw"},{"b":"13.2","h":"20.15","c":"الْمَغْفِرَةِ","d":"ِẗَrِfْغَmْlٱ","e":"ِẗَrِfْغَmْlٱ"},{"b":"15.1","h":"24.15","c":"هُوَ","d":"َwُh","e":"َwُh"},{"b":"15.5","h":"24.66","c":"أَعْلَمُ","d":"ُmَlْʿعَaʾ","e":"ُmَlْʿعَaʾ"},{"b":"16.3","h":"25.94","c":"بِكُمْ","d":"ْmُkِb","e":"ْmُkِb"},{"b":"17.0","h":"26.9","c":"إِذْ","d":"ْhdِiʾ","e":"ْhdِiʾ"},{"b":"17.","h":"27.43","c":"أَنْشَأَكُمْ","d":"mُkَaʾَhsnَaʾ","e":"mُkَaʾَhsnَaʾ"},{"b":"20.0","h":"30.43","c":"مِنَ","d":"َnِّm","e":"َnِّm"},{"b":"20.3","h":"30.93","c":"الْأَرْضِ","d":"ِḍْrَaʾْlٱ","e":"ِḍْrَaʾْlٱ"},{"b":"21.3","h":"32.23","c":"وَإِذْ","d":"ْhdِiʾَw","e":"ْhdِiʾَw"},{"b":"21.9","h":"33.13","c":"أَنْتُمْ","d":"ْmُtnَaʾ","e":"ْmُtnَaʾ"},{"b":"23.5","h":"35.13","c":"أَجِنَّةٌ","d":"ٌẗَّnِjgَaʾ","e":"ٌẗَّnِjgَaʾ"},{"b":"25.9","h":"37.74","c":"فِي","d":"àِf","e":"àِf"},{"b":"26.4","h":"38.53","c":"بُطُونِ","d":"ِnwُṭُb","e":"ِnwُṭُb"},{"b":"27.4","h":"40.89","c":"أُمَّهَاتِكُمْ","d":"ْmُkِtَٰhَّmُaʾ","e":"ْmُkِtَٰhَّmُaʾ"},{"b":"30.5","h":"46.4","c":"فَلَا","d":"āَlَf","e":"āَlَf"},{"b":"31.1","h":"47.22","c":"تُزَكُّوا","d":"۟āٓwُّkَzُt","e":"۟āٓwُّkَzُt"},{"b":"34.1","h":"50.09","c":"أَنْفُسَكُمْ","d":"ْmُkَsُfnَaʾ","e":"ْmُkَsُfnَaʾ"},{"b":"36.","h":"54.5","c":"هُوَ","d":"َwُh","e":"َwُh"},{"b":"37.","h":"54.97","c":"أَعْلَمُ","d":"ُmَlْʿعَaʾ","e":"ُmَlْʿعَaʾ"},{"b":"37.9","h":"56.24","c":"بِمَنِ","d":"ِnَmِb","e":"ِnَmِb"},{"b":"38.6","h":"57.11","c":"اتَّقَى","d":"ٰٓàَqَّtٱ","e":"ٰٓàَqَّtٱ"}],"a":{"g":"Those who avoid the major sins and immoralities, only [committing] slight ones. Indeed, your Lord is vast in forgiveness. He was most knowing of you when He produced you from the earth and when you were fetuses in the wombs of your mothers. So do not claim yourselves to be pure; He is most knowing of who fears Him.","ihya":"\n        <div class=\"ihya-tafsir-box\" style=\"margin-top: 15px; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 10px;\">\n            <h5 style=\"color: #91740c; font-family: Cabin, sans-serif;\">Tafsir Al-Ihya</h5>\n            <div class=\"ihya-arabic\" style=\"font-family: IndoPak; font-size: 18px; text-align: right; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #555;\">\n                بيان ذم العجب وآفاته اعلم أن العجب مذموم في كتاب الله تعالى وسنة رسوله ﭬ. وقد قال تعالى: \"فلا تزكوا أنفسكم\" قال ابن جريج: معناه إذا عملت خيراً فلا تقل عملت. وقال زيد بن أسلم. لا تبروها، أي لا تعتقدوا أنها بارة وهو معنى العجب. وقد قال تعالى \"لا تبطلوا صدقاتكم بالمن والأذى\" والمن نتيجة استعظام الصدقة، واستعظام العمل هو العجب. فظهر بهذا أن العجب مذموم جداً.\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"ihya-english\" style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; color: #777;\">\n                Indeed, the explanation of the censure of self-admiration [al-'ujb] and its destructive consequences. Know that self-admiration [al-'ujb] is censured in the Book of Allah, the Most High, and the Sunnah of His Messenger, peace be upon him. And He, the Most High, has said: \"So do not claim purity for yourselves [fa la tuzakku anfusakum].\" Ibn Jurayj said: Its meaning is, when you perform a good deed, do not say, 'I performed it.' And Zayd ibn Aslam said: Do not declare them righteous, meaning do not believe they are righteous, and this is the meaning of self-admiration [al-'ujb]. And He, the Most High, has said: \"Do not invalidate your charities with reminders of your generosity [al-mann] or injury.\" And the reminder of generosity [al-mann] is the result of magnifying the charity, and magnifying the deed is self-admiration [al-'ujb]. Thus, it becomes clear by this that self-admiration [al-'ujb] is most severely censured.\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        "}},"33":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.55","c":"أَفَرَءَيْتَ","d":"َtْyَءَrَfَaʾ","e":"َtْyَءَrَfَaʾ"},{"b":"1.2","h":"2.25","c":"الَّذِي","d":"àِhdَّlٱ","e":"àِhdَّlٱ"},{"b":"2.1","h":"3.52","c":"تَوَلَّى","d":"ٰàَّlَwَt","e":"ٰàَّlَwَt"}],"a":{"g":"Have you seen the one who turned away"}},"34":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.35","c":"وَأَعْطَى","d":"ٰàَṭْʿعَaʾَw","e":"ٰàَṭْʿعَaʾَw"},{"b":"1.0","h":"1.9","c":"قَلِيلًا","d":"āًlyِlَq","e":"āًlyِlَq"},{"b":"1.9","h":"3.34","c":"وَأَكْدَى","d":"ٰٓàَdْkَaʾَw","e":"ٰٓàَdْkَaʾَw"}],"a":{"g":"And gave a little and [then] refrained?"}},"35":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.35","c":"أَعِنْدَهُ","d":"ۥُhَdnِʿعَaʾ","e":"ۥُhَdnِʿعَaʾ"},{"b":"1.8","h":"2.47","c":"عِلْمُ","d":"ُmْlِʿع","e":"ُmْlِʿع"},{"b":"2.5","h":"3.52","c":"الْغَيْبِ","d":"ِbْyَغْlٱ","e":"ِbْyَغْlٱ"},{"b":"3.3","h":"4.92","c":"فَهُوَ","d":"َwُhَf","e":"َwُhَf"},{"b":"4.0","h":"6","c":"يَرَى","d":"ٰٓàَrَy","e":"ٰٓàَrَy"}],"a":{"g":"Does he have knowledge of the unseen, so he sees?"}},"36":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"1.15","c":"أَمْ","d":"ْmَaʾ","e":"ْmَaʾ"},{"b":"0.38","h":"1.59","c":"لَمْ","d":"ْmَl","e":"ْmَl"},{"b":"0.79","h":"2.16","c":"يُنَبَّأْ","d":"ْaʾَّbَnُy","e":"ْaʾَّbَnُy"},{"b":"1.7","h":"3.74","c":"بِمَا","d":"āَmِb","e":"āَmِb"},{"b":"2.4","h":"4.79","c":"فِي","d":"àِf","e":"àِf"},{"b":"2.9","h":"5.53","c":"صُحُفِ","d":"ِfُḥُṣ","e":"ِfُḥُṣ"},{"b":"3.6","h":"6.61","c":"مُوسَى","d":"ٰàَswُm","e":"ٰàَswُm"}],"a":{"g":"Or has he not been informed of what was in the scriptures of Moses","ihya":"\n        <div class=\"ihya-tafsir-box\" style=\"margin-top: 15px; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 10px;\">\n            <h5 style=\"color: #91740c; font-family: Cabin, sans-serif;\">Tafsir Al-Ihya</h5>\n            <div class=\"ihya-arabic\" style=\"font-family: IndoPak; font-size: 18px; text-align: right; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #555;\">\n                وقال زياد خلوا سبيله، هذا رجل قد لقن حجته.\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"ihya-english\" style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; color: #777;\">\n                And Ziyad said, \"Leave his way, for this is a man whose argument has been instilled [luqqina hujjatuhu].\"\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        "}},"37":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"1","c":"وَإِبْرَاهِيمَ","d":"َmyِhَٰrْbِiʾَw","e":"َmyِhَٰrْbِiʾَw"},{"b":"1.6","h":"3.42","c":"الَّذِي","d":"àِhdَّlٱ","e":"àِhdَّlٱ"},{"b":"2.5","h":"4.83","c":"وَفَّى","d":"ٰٓàَّfَw","e":"ٰٓàَّfَw"}],"a":{"g":"And [of] Abraham, who fulfilled [his obligations] -","ihya":"\n        <div class=\"ihya-tafsir-box\" style=\"margin-top: 15px; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 10px;\">\n            <h5 style=\"color: #91740c; font-family: Cabin, sans-serif;\">Tafsir Al-Ihya</h5>\n            <div class=\"ihya-arabic\" style=\"font-family: IndoPak; font-size: 18px; text-align: right; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #555;\">\n                وروي أنه لما قال جبريل لإبراهيم عليهما السلام وقد رمي إلى النار بالمنجنيق: ألك حاجة؟ قال: أما إليك فلا، وفاءً بقوله حسبي الله ونعم الوكيل، إذا قال ذلك حين أخذ ليرمى، فأنزل الله تعالى: \" وإبراهيم الذي وفى \".\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"ihya-english\" style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; color: #777;\">\n                Indeed, it is narrated that when Gabriel [Jibril], peace be upon them both, said to Abraham [Ibrahim] as he was catapulted into the fire, \"Do you have any need?\" he replied, \"Not from you,\" fulfilling his statement, \"Sufficient for me is Allah [Allah], and He is the best Disposer of affairs [al-Wakil],\" which he had said when he was taken to be thrown. Then Allah, the Exalted, revealed: \"And [of] Abraham who fulfilled [wa-Ibrahim alladhi waffa].\"\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        "}},"38":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.65","c":"أَلَّا","d":"āَّlَaʾ","e":"āَّlَaʾ"},{"b":"0.8","h":"1.84","c":"تَزِرُ","d":"ُrِzَt","e":"ُrِzَt"},{"b":"1.5","h":"2.97","c":"وَازِرَةٌ","d":"ٌẗَrِzāَw","e":"ٌẗَrِzāَw"},{"b":"3.4","h":"5.35","c":"وِزْرَ","d":"َrْzِw","e":"َrْzِw"},{"b":"4.1","h":"6.33","c":"أُخْرَى","d":"ٰàَrْhkُaʾ","e":"ٰàَrْhkُaʾ"}],"a":{"g":"That no bearer of burdens will bear the burden of another"}},"39":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.85","c":"وَأَنْ","d":"nَaʾَw","e":"nَaʾَw"},{"b":"0.33","h":"1.33","c":"لَيْسَ","d":"َsْyَّl","e":"َsْyَّl"},{"b":"1.2","h":"2.74","c":"لِلْإِنْسَانِ","d":"ِnَٰsnِiʾْlِl","e":"ِnَٰsnِiʾْlِl"},{"b":"3.6","h":"5.64","c":"إِلَّا","d":"āَّlِiʾ","e":"āَّlِiʾ"},{"b":"4.5","h":"7.03","c":"مَا","d":"āَm","e":"āَm"},{"b":"4.8","h":"7.83","c":"سَعَى","d":"ٰàَʿعَs","e":"ٰàَʿعَs"}],"a":{"g":"And that there is not for man except that [good] for which he strives","ihya":"\n        <div class=\"ihya-tafsir-box\" style=\"margin-top: 15px; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 10px;\">\n            <h5 style=\"color: #91740c; font-family: Cabin, sans-serif;\">Tafsir Al-Ihya</h5>\n            <div class=\"ihya-arabic\" style=\"font-family: IndoPak; font-size: 18px; text-align: right; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #555;\">\n                وقال في أمر الآخرة وأن ليس للإنسان إلا ما سعى فقد تكفل لك بأمر الدنيا خاصة وصرفك عن السعى فيها فكذبته بأفعالك وأصبحت تتكالبين على طلبها تكالب المدهوش المستهتر ووكل أمر الآخرة إلى سعيك فأعرضت عنها إعراض المغرور المستحقر.\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"ihya-english\" style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; color: #777;\">\n                Indeed, concerning the matter of the Hereafter [al-akhirah] and that for man there is only what he strives for, He has guaranteed for you the matter of the world [al-dunya] specifically and diverted you from striving in it. Yet you have belied Him with your actions, and you have become one who scrambles in pursuit of it, scrambling like one who is bewildered and heedless. And He has entrusted the matter of the Hereafter [al-akhirah] to your striving, yet you have turned away from it, turning away like one who is deluded and contemptuous.\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        "}},"40":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.85","c":"وَأَنَّ","d":"َّnَaʾَw","e":"َّnَaʾَw"},{"b":"1.2","h":"2.28","c":"سَعْيَهُ","d":"ۥُhَyْʿعَs","e":"ۥُhَyْʿعَs"},{"b":"2.4","h":"4.09","c":"سَوْفَ","d":"َfْwَs","e":"َfْwَs"},{"b":"3.0","h":"5.2","c":"يُرَى","d":"ٰàَrُy","e":"ٰàَrُy"}],"a":{"g":"And that his effort is going to be seen -"}},"41":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.35","c":"ثُمَّ","d":"َّmُht","e":"َّmُht"},{"b":"1.0","h":"1.61","c":"يُجْزَاهُ","d":"ُhٰàَzْjgُy","e":"ُhٰàَzْjgُy"},{"b":"2.1","h":"3.3","c":"الْجَزَاءَ","d":"َءٓāَzَjgْlٱ","e":"َءٓāَzَjgْlٱ"},{"b":"4.7","h":"5.87","c":"الْأَوْفَى","d":"ٰàَfْwَaʾْlٱ","e":"ٰàَfْwَaʾْlٱ"}],"a":{"g":"Then he will be recompensed for it with the fullest recompense"}},"42":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.61","c":"وَأَنَّ","d":"َّnَaʾَw","e":"َّnَaʾَw"},{"b":"1.4","h":"2.02","c":"إِلَى","d":"ٰàَlِiʾ","e":"ٰàَlِiʾ"},{"b":"2.1","h":"3.06","c":"رَبِّكَ","d":"َkِّbَr","e":"َkِّbَr"},{"b":"3.0","h":"4.68","c":"الْمُنْتَهَى","d":"ٰàَhَtnُmْlٱ","e":"ٰàَhَtnُmْlٱ"}],"a":{"g":"And that to your Lord is the finality"}},"43":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.5","c":"وَأَنَّهُ","d":"ۥُhَّnَaʾَw","e":"ۥُhَّnَaʾَw"},{"b":"1.8","h":"2.64","c":"هُوَ","d":"َwُh","e":"َwُh"},{"b":"2.2","h":"3.33","c":"أَضْحَكَ","d":"َkَḥْḍَaʾ","e":"َkَḥْḍَaʾ"},{"b":"3.1","h":"4.82","c":"وَأَبْكَى","d":"ٰàَkْbَaʾَw","e":"ٰàَkْbَaʾَw"}],"a":{"g":"And that it is He who makes [one] laugh and weep"}},"44":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.65","c":"وَأَنَّهُ","d":"ۥُhَّnَaʾَw","e":"ۥُhَّnَaʾَw"},{"b":"1.9","h":"2.78","c":"هُوَ","d":"َwُh","e":"َwُh"},{"b":"2.2","h":"3.5","c":"أَمَاتَ","d":"َtāَmَaʾ","e":"َtāَmَaʾ"},{"b":"3.2","h":"4.98","c":"وَأَحْيَا","d":"āَyْḥَaʾَw","e":"āَyْḥَaʾَw"}],"a":{"g":"And that it is He who causes death and gives life"}},"45":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.6","c":"وَأَنَّهُ","d":"ۥُhَّnَaʾَw","e":"ۥُhَّnَaʾَw"},{"b":"1.8","h":"2.82","c":"خَلَقَ","d":"َqَlَhk","e":"َqَlَhk"},{"b":"2.5","h":"3.9","c":"الزَّوْجَيْنِ","d":"ِnْyَjgْwَّzlٱ","e":"ِnْyَjgْwَّzlٱ"},{"b":"4.1","h":"6.26","c":"الذَّكَرَ","d":"َrَkَّhdlٱ","e":"َrَkَّhdlٱ"},{"b":"4.8","h":"7.25","c":"وَالْأُنْثَى","d":"ٰàَhtnُaʾْlٱَw","e":"ٰàَhtnُaʾْlٱَw"}],"a":{"g":"And that He creates the two mates - the male and female -"}},"46":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.7","c":"مِنْ","d":"nِm","e":"nِm"},{"b":"0.99","h":"1.82","c":"نُطْفَةٍ","d":"ٍẗَfْṭُّn","e":"ٍẗَfْṭُّn"},{"b":"1.9","h":"3.4","c":"إِذَا","d":"āَhdِiʾ","e":"āَhdِiʾ"},{"b":"2.6","h":"4.41","c":"تُمْنَى","d":"ٰàَnْmُt","e":"ٰàَnْmُt"}],"a":{"g":"From a sperm-drop when it is emitted"}},"47":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.06","c":"وَأَنَّ","d":"َّnَaʾَw","e":"َّnَaʾَw"},{"b":"1.2","h":"1.42","c":"عَلَيْهِ","d":"ِhْyَlَʿع","e":"ِhْyَlَʿع"},{"b":"2.3","h":"2.85","c":"النَّشْأَةَ","d":"َẗَaʾْhsَّnlٱ","e":"َẗَaʾْhsَّnlٱ"},{"b":"4.0","h":"4.73","c":"الْأُخْرَى","d":"ٰàَrْhkُaʾْlٱ","e":"ٰàَrْhkُaʾْlٱ"}],"a":{"g":"And that [incumbent] upon Him is the next creation"}},"48":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"1.15","c":"وَأَنَّهُ","d":"ۥُhَّnَaʾَw","e":"ۥُhَّnَaʾَw"},{"b":"2.1","h":"3.27","c":"هُوَ","d":"َwُh","e":"َwُh"},{"b":"2.5","h":"3.97","c":"أَغْنَى","d":"ٰàَnْغَaʾ","e":"ٰàَnْغَaʾ"},{"b":"3.4","h":"5.41","c":"وَأَقْنَى","d":"ٰàَnْqَaʾَw","e":"ٰàَnْqَaʾَw"}],"a":{"g":"And that it is He who enriches and suffices"}},"49":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.8","c":"وَأَنَّهُ","d":"ۥُhَّnَaʾَw","e":"ۥُhَّnَaʾَw"},{"b":"1.7","h":"2.75","c":"هُوَ","d":"َwُh","e":"َwُh"},{"b":"2.1","h":"3.48","c":"رَبُّ","d":"ُّbَr","e":"ُّbَr"},{"b":"2.8","h":"4.55","c":"الشِّعْرَى","d":"ٰàَrْʿعِّhslٱ","e":"ٰàَrْʿعِّhslٱ"}],"a":{"g":"And that it is He who is the Lord of Sirius"}},"50":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.55","c":"وَأَنَّهُ","d":"ٓۥُhَّnَaʾَw","e":"ٓۥُhَّnَaʾَw"},{"b":"2.9","h":"3.62","c":"أَهْلَكَ","d":"َkَlْhَaʾ","e":"َkَlْhَaʾ"},{"b":"3.7","h":"4.87","c":"عَادًا","d":"āًdāَʿع","e":"āًdāَʿع"},{"b":"4.5","h":"6.37","c":"الْأُولَى","d":"ٰàَlwُaʾْlٱ","e":"ٰàَlwُaʾْlٱ"}],"a":{"g":"And that He destroyed the first [people of] 'Aad"}},"51":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.85","c":"وَثَمُودَ","d":"۟āَdwُmَhtَw","e":"۟āَdwُmَhtَw"},{"b":"1.1","h":"2.46","c":"فَمَا","d":"ٓāَmَf","e":"ٓāَmَf"},{"b":"3.4","h":"4.64","c":"أَبْقَى","d":"ٰàَqْbَaʾ","e":"ٰàَqْbَaʾ"}],"a":{"g":"And Thamud - and He did not spare [them] -"}},"52":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.69","c":"وَقَوْمَ","d":"َmْwَqَw","e":"َmْwَqَw"},{"b":"0.85","h":"1.95","c":"نُوحٍ","d":"ٍḥwُn","e":"ٍḥwُn"},{"b":"2.4","h":"4.14","c":"مِنْ","d":"nِّm","e":"nِّm"},{"b":"3.7","h":"5.23","c":"قَبْلُ","d":"ُlْbَq","e":"ُlْbَq"},{"b":"4.7","h":"7.8","c":"إِنَّهُمْ","d":"ْmُhَّnِiʾ","e":"ْmُhَّnِiʾ"},{"b":"6.6","h":"9.69","c":"كَانُوا","d":"۟āwُnāَk","e":"۟āwُnāَk"},{"b":"7.5","h":"11.2","c":"هُمْ","d":"ْmُh","e":"ْmُh"},{"b":"8.0","h":"11.95","c":"أَظْلَمَ","d":"َmَlْẓَaʾ","e":"َmَlْẓَaʾ"},{"b":"8.9","h":"13.41","c":"وَأَطْغَى","d":"ٰàَغْṭَaʾَw","e":"ٰàَغْṭَaʾَw"}],"a":{"g":"And the people of Noah before. Indeed, it was they who were [even] more unjust and oppressing."}},"53":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.9","c":"وَالْمُؤْتَفِكَةَ","d":"َẗَkِfَtْwʾُmْlٱَw","e":"َẗَkِfَtْwʾُmْlٱَw"},{"b":"1.8","h":"3.54","c":"أَهْوَى","d":"ٰàَwْhَaʾ","e":"ٰàَwْhَaʾ"}],"a":{"g":"And the overturned towns He hurled down"}},"54":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.8","c":"فَغَشَّاهَا","d":"āَhٰàَّhsَغَf","e":"āَhٰàَّhsَغَf"},{"b":"1.5","h":"3.31","c":"مَا","d":"āَm","e":"āَm"},{"b